trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of print system objects.
trans-unit.target: 表示列印系統物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: If you derive a class from <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObject>, you may want to derive a collection of objects of that class from PrintSystemObjects.
trans-unit.target: 如果您是衍生自<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObject>，您可能想要從 PrintSystemObjects 衍生的物件，該類別的集合。</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObject>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > 類別內<xref:System.Printing>命名空間不支援為 Windows 服務或 ASP.NET 應用程式或服務中使用。</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Attempting to use these classes from within one of these application types may produce unexpected problems, such as diminished service performance and run-time exceptions.
trans-unit.target: 嘗試使用這些類別時，這些應用程式類型的其中一個內可能會產生無法預期的問題，例如會受到影響服務的效能和執行階段例外狀況。

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Forms application, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: 如果您想要從 Windows Form 應用程式列印，請參閱<xref:System.Drawing.Printing>命名空間。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 所使用的資源全部釋出<xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>.
trans-unit.target: 當您完成使用<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>呼叫 Dispose

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Dispose 方法會使<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>中無法使用的狀態。</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: 在呼叫 Dispose 之後，您必須釋放所有參考<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>讓記憶體回收行程可以回收記憶體的<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>所佔用。</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[清除 Unmanaged 資源上](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)和[實作 Dispose 方法](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 永遠呼叫 Dispose 之後，再放開您的最後一個參考至<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>。</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> object's <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 否則，它所使用的資源將不會釋放直到記憶體回收行程呼叫<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>物件的<xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>方法。</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: 所使用的 unmanaged 的資源釋出<xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects"></xref>並選擇性釋放 managed 的資源。

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會呼叫公用<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose>方法和<xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>方法。</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> invokes the protected Dispose method with the unnamed Boolean parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose>未命名的布林參數設定為與叫用受保護的 Dispose 方法`true`。</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes Dispose with the parameter set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>將參數設定為與叫用 Dispose `false`。</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the Boolean parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> references.
trans-unit.target: 布林值參數時`true`，這個方法的任何 managed 物件所持有的資源全部釋出這個<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>參考。</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會叫用`Dispose()`每個參考物件的方法。

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: 即將加入。
